And all I am is a man
I want the world in my hands
I hate the beach, but I stand
In California with my toes in the sand
Use the sleeves of my sweater
let's have an adventure
Head in the clouds, but my gravity's centered
Touch my neck and I'll touch yours
You in those little high-waisted shorts, oh

She knows what I think about
And what I think about
One love, two mouths
One love, one house
No shirt, no blouse
Just us, you find out
Nothing that I wouldn't 
wanna tell you about, no

'Cause it's too cold for you here and now
So let me hold both your hands 
in the holes of my sweater

I don't mind if there's not much to say
Sometimes the silence guides a mind
To move to a place so far away
The goosebumps start to raise
The minute that my left hand meets your waist
And then I watch your face
Put my finger on your tongue 
'cause you love the taste, yeah
These hearts adore
Everyone the other beats hardest for
Inside, this place is warm
Outside, it starts to pour

Woah, woah

So let me hold both your hands 
in the holes of my sweater
'Cause it's too cold for you here and now
Let me hold both your hands 
in the holes of my sweater

[Outro]
And it's too cold, it's too cold
The holes of my sweater

snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV – "Back to War" In-Engine Trailer | PC Gaming Show Tokyo Direct
snippet.description:
Here’s your official look into the next evolution of the iconic real-time strategy franchise with Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV!
First revealed during PC Gaming Show: Tokyo Direct, this new trailer has been captured entirely from in-engine gameplay. 

Many years after the events of Dawn of War: Dark Crusade, Kronus burns as Space Marines of the Blood Ravens Chapter and their Adeptus Mechanicus allies clash with brutal Ork hordes. With victory almost certain, a new threat emerges: the Necrons. As this new faction overwhelms the battlefield, the Imperium must rebuild and grow their forces if they hope to stand a chance. 

Whether you’re a long-time fan of the series or brand new to the world of Dawn of War, this new trailer, captured entirely in-engine, provides a more detailed look at what to expect with exciting gameplay, action-packed cinematics, and a taste of the war-torn future that awaits.

At last, back to war! 
---

Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV releases on Steam in 2026!

snippet.title: Black Panther 3 (2025) - First Trailer | Denzel Washington, Will Smith
snippet.description:
#blackpanther #blackpanther3 #willsmith 

Smith and Washington rumored to redefine Wakanda’s fate in Black Panther.

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
✅ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

🎥 Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies (Google Veo 3), movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! 🍿

🐈‍⬛  Black Panther 3: New Wakanda

Speculation has begun swirling around the possibility of Black Panther 3, with rumors pointing to Will Smith and Denzel Washington stepping into pivotal new roles. The third chapter is expected to explore Wakanda’s place in a changing world, while also introducing new figures that could reshape the kingdom’s legacy. With Smith and Washington involved, fans are already imagining a blend of emotional gravitas and powerful performances that could carry the franchise in new directions.

Sources suggest that Smith’s rumored character could be tied to global politics or perhaps an ally-turned-rival of Wakanda, while Washington’s potential role is whispered to have deeper connections to history and leadership. The film may explore themes of legacy, family, and power, as Wakanda continues to face challenges both within and beyond its borders. Audiences are eager to see how the chemistry between these two actors might shape the story’s most dramatic moments.

There is speculation that the setting may expand beyond Wakanda’s borders, delving into other nations and global stakes. The combination of Smith’s charisma and Washington’s commanding presence could offer one of the most compelling chapters in Marvel’s upcoming slate. If true, Black Panther 3 would not only continue the franchise but also honor its themes of unity, resilience, and responsibility in an uncertain world.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: Kaiju Cleanup - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Relax and unwind by cleaning up the world’s biggest corpses. Here's your look at Kaiju Cleanup announcement trailer for the upcoming cleaning simulation game. Kaiju Cleanup will be available on PC.

When colossal alien titans run rampant until getting domed by a railgun, the world finds itself in need of a true hero. That’s you: a Kaiju Cleaner who won’t be perturbed by petty concerns like “workplace injury” or “life expectancy”. After another Kaiju attack on the city, use your tools to clean up vast piles of dead monster until the zone is safe for reconstruction. The Kaiju may be dead, but its corpse is leaking radiation, seeping acidic fluids, concealing explosive organs, and generally making the area inhospitable to any other form of life. You’ll probably die as you go about your work, but that’s fine; send another clone, mop up your corpse, and carry on.

snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We’re updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

American Sign Language: https://www.youtube.com/live/W3uQA_unm0I
British Sign Language: https://youtube.com/live/ZygMYm2sx5U
Audio Descriptions: https://youtube.com/live/DoXrLv__PAY

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!  
https://www.minecraft.net/
